          "id": "fu-slide-1",
          "title": "Start with the singular future endings",
          "description": "The future uses `doon`, and the ending changes by person. Notice that `I` and `he` share one ending, while `you` and `she` share another.",
          "focusPoints": [
            "Use `doonaa` with `I` and `he`",
            "Use `doontaa` with `you` and `she`",
            "Keep the verb stem steady while you watch the ending"
